{"tid":1697974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"性暴力調查：三人被迫性交","createTime":"2019-11-07T07:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T08:43:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d4092930b6b4b023095515b69adfb7eaf9f38855","tid":1697974,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191107/IH3JUZFPMFQNIRKWPQ7TZOT3LI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191107%2FIH3JUZFPMFQNIRKWPQ7TZOT3LI%2F&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=49704a87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191107%2FIH3JUZFPMFQNIRKWPQ7TZOT3LI%2F&h=c4784bce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191107/IH3JUZFPMFQNIRKWPQ7TZOT3LI/</a><br />\n<br />\n性暴力調查：三人被迫性交<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191107/large/1573063830_4c3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191107%2Flarge%2F1573063830_4c3c.jpg&h=684eb49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數十名市民昨戴上口罩到場聲援吳傲雪。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】關注婦女性暴力協會昨發表「反送中運動的性暴力經驗調查」，逾80%人曾遭有性意味說話挑釁、侮辱或恐嚇，有三人更曾被迫性交。32人指施暴者為警方或其他執法部門，但只有極少數人選擇報警，主因是認為交警方處理成效不大。協會表示，政府必須從速成立獨立調查機關，調查運動期間所發生的性暴力個案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受害人憂報警反被控<br />\n<br />\n協會8至9月透過自填式方法收集問卷，共67人表示在運動期間遭受性暴力，程度由侮辱謾罵至非法性交。受訪者包括示威者、一般途人或街坊、救護員、記者或攝影師等，大部份為女性，亦有九名男性。當中29人遭受性暴力多於一次，11人更高達五次或以上。逾80%人表示曾遭有性意味說話挑釁、侮辱或恐嚇，其次為有意或無意觸碰身體敏感部位、以色迷迷目光注視或偷窺等，當中三人在受威脅或嚇逼情況下非法性交。32人表示施暴者為警方或其他執法人員，其餘是政府或建制派支持者。<br />\n<br />\n調查發現，36人指事發地點在街上，12人稱事發地點為警署或收押所；只有兩人選擇報警，逾77%人不報警原因是認為警方處理成效不大，過半人擔心被警方反控其他罪名，另有27人因施暴者為警方或其他執法人員而不報警。協會總幹事王秀容指，政府、執法部門與民眾陷入缺乏互信局面，受害人難踏出求助的一步，建議受害者可在毋須報警下進行法醫取證，確保公義不會無法彰顯。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張文鈴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/rzJseOMq7YGwX5glVRQF1wpW004=/802x439/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/UFFKOAKWIN5QSKROCSQHNATHRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FrzJseOMq7YGwX5glVRQF1wpW004%3D%2F802x439%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FUFFKOAKWIN5QSKROCSQHNATHRE.jpg&h=bbf9e423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"cdf92f28ddbf2f0987615bc5db7abd766abd12cc","tid":1697974,"uid":65847,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"咩叫被迫性交？強姦就強姦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68faf59ace0f829f722bcc99e930956b07e91adb","tid":1697974,"uid":35378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cdf92f28ddbf2f0987615bc5db7abd766abd12cc","tid":1697974,"uid":65847,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"咩叫被迫性交？強姦就強姦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:00:52.000Z","msg":"睇番之前有講過<br />\n<br />\n可能意思係迫兩個不相識嘅被捕者性交"},{"pid":"1fbbea7af7dc4420503aeba34b72cb22e7e46278","tid":1697974,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68faf59ace0f829f722bcc99e930956b07e91adb","tid":1697974,"uid":35378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cdf92f28ddbf2f0987615bc5db7abd766abd12cc","tid":1697974,"uid":65847,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"咩叫被迫性交？強姦就強姦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:00:52.000Z","msg":"睇番之前有講過<br />\n<br />\n可能意思係迫兩個不相識嘅被捕者性交"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"啲警甴當自己睇緊av咁"},{"pid":"1f8a2815b80d7a0382f0e4e3f7045e3238f56b1e","tid":1697974,"uid":172345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:08:25.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"},{"pid":"ddbfffc710a8f5339ada2be46a87e09af959c5bb","tid":16