"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:22:10.000Z","msg":"非自願性交不外乎<br />\n1) 要你&quot;自願&quot;被黑警直接黎<br />\n2) 要你同唔相識既人黎，但要你另一半睇住<br />\n3) 明知你地係伴侶，要你地係其他人面對搞<br />\n4) 唔夠秤，都照搞<br />\n<br />\n除左3之外，應該另外3個都有可能"},{"pid":"381588946f079f770d427144e21248ff44a90389","tid":1697974,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"冇嘢幫到手<br />\n只可以勸女手足唔好企咁前，遠離曱甴，唔好落單"},{"pid":"56eb9b787421a8f54a2c75550d7835ef2cc33e5e","tid":1697974,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}